Title: Dalan Therapy Liquid Soap Combo Pack of White Tea & Aloe Vera and Chocolate Milk and Cocoa Butter Hand Wash
Description: One of the best international fragrances, mild white tea aroma coupled with moisture rich Aloevera - Leaves your hands well moisturized and fragranced. Aloe vera is a cactus plant that belongs to the Liliaceae family. It grows in dry climates such as those found in parts of Africa and India and has been used medicinally for centuries. Aloe leaves secrete a clear gel that when broken off from the rest of the plant that can be applied topically to heal wounds and soothe skin. Aloe moisturizes the skin without giving it a greasy feel, so it`s perfect for anyone with an oily skin complexion. As we age, everyone begins to worry about the appearance of fine lines and the loss of elasticity in their skin. Aloe leaves contain a plethora of antioxidants including, beta carotene, vitamin C and E that can help improve the skin's natural firmness and keep the skin hydrated. Aloe vera or aloe-based products come in handy in summers as well as winters. Its cooling properties provide instant relief from sunburns in the summer by hydrating the skin and in winters, it helps get rid of dryness by adding moisture to the skin. White tea is known for its antioxidants, antiseptic and preventive properties. Free radicals from staying out in the sun too long, stress, and a poor diet can damage the skin and cause it to prematurely age. By scavenging these free radicals, white tea protects the skin and helps to reverse some of the damage. One of the best international fragrances, Rich Cocoa Butter aroma coupled with moisture rich Chocolate milk - Leaves your hands well moisturized and fragranced. Cocoa Butter, also called Cacao Butter, is the cream-colored fat extracted from cacao seeds (cocoa beans) and used to add flavor, scent, and smoothness to chocolate, cosmetics, tanning oil, soap, and a multitude of topical lotions and creams. Cocoa Butter has been called the ultimate moisturizer, and has been used to keep skin soft and supple for centuries. Cocoa Butter contains a number of different antioxidants that can kill off a wide range of different free radicals that destroy your skin cells and lead to premature aging. This makes it an ideal skin care product. The moisturizing of milk and chocolate aroma makes this liquid soap just right to take a chocolaty ride! Sold in over 30+ countries across the Americas, Europe, Africa, Asia, Australia and New Zealand. Dalan products are now available in India through our sole importer M/s Soumya and has also been approved by CDSCO, the sole drug control authority in India for regulation of imported cosmetics in India.

Title: Jordana LSN Lipstick 3.4 g(Cherry Pie)
Description: LSN Lipstick by Jordana is an excellent product that glides on your lips seamlessly, and gives soft shine finish. This creamy rich formula is very easy to use and offers long wearing. The best part is this product is that it does not smudge off your lips & onto your teeth. Best Suitable For - All types of lips. Tips and Tricks ? Open your mouth and start from the center of upper and lower lip. Fill in your lipstick on the lips in an outward direction. Blot out the excess oil of your lips with a tissue paper. Made in the United States of America.

Title: Jordana Lipstick 3.4(Oro)
Description: Jordana Lipsticks help keep your lips soft and supple, with beautiful, dazzling colors. These are rich and creamy and give soft shiny finish to your lips. The best part is these do not smudge off your lips and onto your teeth. This ultra rich formula makes your lips soft and looks glossy. You can find a Jordana Lipstick for every style, every mood, every occasion or every look. These lipsticks come in .12oz/3.4g. Best Suitable For - All types of lips Tips and Tricks - Apply a little amount of your foundation before applying your lipstick. Foundation even out your lipstick and helps it to last longer. Open your mouth & start from the center of upper & lower lip. Fill in your lipstick on the lips in an outward direction. Blot out the excess oil of your lips with a tissue paper.
